Title: Provides maternity patients with information regarding births utilizing forceps
Summary: Provides maternity patients with information regarding births utilizing forceps including any potential injuries the mother or child could sustain due to the use of forceps and statistics on deaths resulting from the use of forceps.
LawCode: Amd ยง2803-j, Pub Health L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law, in relation to providing maternity patients with information regarding births utilizing forceps
